## ğŸ“ TROUBLESHOOTING QUICK LINKS

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| Syntax error in file | Check indentation, brackets, colons |
| Wizard won't launch | Verify Python, check import errors |
| Paths screen missing | Verify screen list updated to 5 items |
| Model duplicates remain | Check dedup logic in get_installed_models() |
| Config not saving | Verify _on_finish() calls create_config() |
| Browse button doesn't work | Check filedialog imported from tkinter |
| Still shows AetherMUD | Search for "AetherMUD", should find 0 |

